graph LR
    %% --- ACTORS & FRONTEND ---
    P((Patient))
    D((Doctor))
    S((Specialist))
    AD((Admin))

    LP[Landing Page]
    PD[Patient Dashboard]
    DD[Doctor Dashboard]
    SD[Specialist Dashboard]
    AD_UI[Admin Dashboard]

    %% --- API LAYER ---
    GW[AWS API Gateway]

    %% --- CORE SERVICES ---
    AUTH[Auth & User Service]
    SUB[Subscription Service]
    APPT[Appointment Service]
    CLIN[Clinical Service]
    WALLET[Wallet & Payment Service]
    STORE[Store Service]
    COMM[Communication Service]

    %% --- DATA LAYER ---
    DB[(Primary Database)]
    CACHE[(Redis Cache)]
    S3[(S3 Storage)]

    %% --- EXTERNAL ---
    STRIPE[Stripe API]
    WS[WebSocket Server]

    %% --- CONNECTIONS ---
    P --> LP & PD
    D --> DD
    S --> SD
    AD --> AD_UI

    LP & PD & DD & SD & AD_UI -->|HTTPS| GW

    GW --> AUTH
    GW --> SUB
    GW --> APPT
    GW --> CLIN
    GW --> WALLET
    GW --> STORE
    GW --> COMM

    AUTH & SUB & APPT & CLIN & WALLET & STORE -->|Read/Write| DB
    AUTH & SUB -->|Session/Cache| CACHE
    
    WALLET <-->|Payments/Payouts| STRIPE
    APPT & CLIN & AUTH -->|Documents/Images| S3
    COMM <-->|Real-time Chat| WS

    %% --- ANNOTATIONS (Mimicking the green text in your image) ---
    
    subgraph Annotations ["Technical Notes & Logic"]
        direction TB
        N1["<b>Subscription Middleware:</b><br/>Intercepts /doctors/:id/profile.<br/>If plan='none' -> 403 Forbidden.<br/>If plan='standard' -> Return Data."]
        N2["<b>Wallet Logic:</b><br/>Stripe Webhook -> Credit Admin.<br/>Calculate Platform Fee.<br/>Credit Remainder to User Wallet."]
        N3["<b>Document Security:</b><br/>Doctor licenses stored in S3.<br/>Served via Pre-signed URLs<br/>(expire in 15 mins)."]
    end

    SUB -.-> N1
    WALLET -.-> N2
    AUTH -.-> N3